Name: Cube Projection
About the game: This is a game that tests the imagination of three-dimensional space. Just find the projection of the cube in the front view and left view direction, and then clicks the corresponding grid above to pass the game. If you don't understand, you can click the help button in the upper right corner, there will be a projected prompt animation. In the later difficult levels, you can also rotate the cube to observe.
